            "notes": "The deck focuses on a combination of aggressive play and graveyard recursion. It utilizes cards like Exhume, Animate Dead, and Corpse Dance to bring back powerful creatures from the graveyard, such as Griselbrand and Archon of Cruelty, to pressure opponents. The deck also includes disruptive spells like Duress and Thoughtseize to control the opponent's hand and keep them from building up a board state. Additionally, there are spells like Gloomlake Verge and Urborg, Tomb of Yawgmoth to generate mana and fix the deck's colors. Overall, the strategy revolves around fast, aggressive plays backed up by graveyard manipulation and disruption to outpace and overwhelm the opponent in a 1 vs 1 duel format."
